casebody.data:
Renee D. BELL, petitioner,
v.
ORLANDO HEALTH, INC., dba Winnie Palmer Hospital. No. 18-6523. Supreme Court of the United States Jan. 7, 2019.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the District Court of Appeal of Florida, Fifth District dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
